<p>I'm using the following code so the user can take a pic:</p>  <pre><code>- (IBAction)takePhoto:(UIButton *)sender {      UIImagePickerController *picker = [[UIImagePickerController alloc] init];     picker.delegate = self;     picker.allowsEditing = YES;     picker.sourceType = UIImagePickerControllerSourceTypeCamera;      [self presentViewController:picker animated:YES completion:NULL];  } </code></pre>  <p>Is there a way to make the camera occupy the hole screen?</p>